  "notes": [
    {
      "id": 0,
      "x": 50,
      "y": 1300,
      "title": "📊 Equb Database ER Diagram v2",
      "content": "Complete database schema for the Equb savings & lottery app.\n\n🔑 **11 Tables:**\n• users — Members and admins\n• slots — Membership slots per tier category\n• payments — Daily payment schedule per slot\n• payment_logs — Payment audit trail (denormalized user_name for history)\n• draws — Draw/raffle records (FK to slots added)\n• savings_transactions — Savings deposits & withdrawals\n• sms_logs — Outbound SMS history\n• settings — Key-value app configuration\n• personal_access_tokens — Sanctum API auth (NEW)\n• password_reset_tokens — Password reset OTP storage (NEW)\n• sessions — Laravel web sessions (NEW)\n\n✅ **Improvements made (vs v1):**\n1. Added 3 framework tables (Sanctum, sessions, password_resets)\n2. Added CHECK constraints on all monetary/count fields (>=0 or >0)\n3. Added FK draws.slot_id → slots.id for referential integrity\n4. ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP on all updated_at columns\n5. Added composite indexes for real query patterns\n6. UNIQUE (category, slot_number) instead of global slot_number\n7. CHECK (amount > 0) on savings_transactions\n8. Expanded payments unique to (slot_id, day_index, user_id)\n9. Added indexes on unique_payment_code & payout_code\n10. Documented denormalization justification in comments",
      "color": "#ffffff",
      "height": 380
    }
  ],
